{"tid":1087701,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗傷情嚴重,趕唔到打阿積士","createTime":"2019-04-01T13:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T11:09:21.000Z","uid":173952,"like":32,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f14f87c3af3ff2a087e8c3deb0ca736ce0f91c","tid":1087701,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T13:49:24.000Z","msg":"尤文主帥阿萊格里在客戰卡利亞裡的賽前記者會上更新了球隊傷情，他稱&Ccedil;羅很難趕上對陣阿賈克斯的首回合比賽。<br />\n&ldquo;C羅正在努力復出，我們希望他能為對陣阿賈克斯的比賽做好準備，但很難。科斯塔情況不錯，應該能踢那場比賽。赫迪拉昨天訓練了，可能在對陣米蘭的比賽中復出。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;誇德拉多練得不錯，回歸只是時間問題。今天我們會看看迪巴拉的情況如何。曼祖基奇有點感冒，需要檢查下他的情況。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;佩林的肩膀被撞了一下，踢不了卡利亞裡了，但希望能趕上對陣阿賈克斯。<br />\n&ldquo;斯皮納佐拉的膝蓋有點問題，會缺陣一段時間。巴爾扎利回歸訓練了。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"2f04ca0b6295720192d858f0493d22decc4671fc","tid":1087701,"uid":155902,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T13:50:12.000Z","msg":"佢臨尾出10分鐘夠贏la"},{"pid":"38aed877cdc28846f0f0b35a8fe079267b04a5b6","tid":1087701,"uid":90515,"like":98,"dislike":17,"score":81,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T13:51:02.000Z","msg":"唔踢咁贏硬了，詳細請參考2016葡萄牙"},{"pid":"a95e855ba3eb1857abc3531e24c221296e2bd54d","tid":1087701,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38aed877cdc28846f0f0b35a8fe079267b04a5b6","tid":1087701,"uid":90515,"like":98,"dislike":17,"score":81,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T13:51:02.000Z","msg":"唔踢咁贏硬了，詳細請參考2016葡萄牙"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T13:52:40.000Z","msg":"拖單都要企埋一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3f874d54269b13ead4625ab6b6f6e2bd4605f4","tid":1087701,"uid":219990,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T13:56:34.000Z","msg":"又係場邊激勵隊友，四連冠不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ba61191c80a4acb90d2a37d496f6e194279563","tid":1087701,"uid":90515,"like":14,"dislike":6,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a95e855ba3eb1857abc3531e24c221296e2bd54d","tid":